  "text": "Two important questions regarding q-Gaussian distributions have been recently raised by Douxois (2007) : if q-Gaussian law describes physical phenomena and if the entropic q parameter could be predicted in terms of microscopic parameters. [CITATION_1] , has answered these questions reviewing the present state of nonextensive statistical mechanics and reporting analytical relations for the parameter q that have appeared over the recent years. It is our opinion that natural field of application and validation of q-Gaussian distributions is astrophysics and space science.",
