      "title": "Non-Gaussian distributions under scrutiny\" under scrutiny",
      "abstract": "Comment of the very interesting paper by Hilhorst&Schehr, J. Stat. Mech. P06003 (2007). The main point is that one should be extremely careful when interpreting non-Gaussian data in terms of q-Gaussians."
